comments: Kleber (DAL) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Randle (NYK) during his drive.
Gibson (NYK) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Doncic's (DAL) drive to the basket.
Gibson (NYK) moves into Doncic's (DAL) body and the contact affects his shot attempt.
FInney-Smith (DAL) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Morris Sr. (NYK) during his drive.
Morris Sr. (NYK) ends his dribble with a jump stop, after which he may pivot on either foot.  Morris Sr. moves his left foot, establishing his right as his pivot foot and he maintains his pivot foot.
Finney-Smith (DAL) legally contests Morris Sr.'s (NYK) shot attempt.
Doncic (DAL) and Barrett (NYK) make incidental contact with one another off ball.
Ntilikina (NYK) is moving alongside Hardaway Jr.'s (DAL) path and he maintains a legal guarding position on the perimeter.

Hardaway Jr. (DAL) ends his dribble and does not take more than two steps after his gather.  Additionally, the ball is cleanly deflected by Ntilikina (NYK), and Hardaway Jr. (DAL) does not dribble with both hands on the ball.
Kleber (DAL) is jumping alongside Randle's (NYK) path to the basket, and there is no conclusive camera angle that shows if Kleber makes contact to Randle's head.
Finney-Smith (DAL) makes contact to Gibson's (NYK) head as he defends the shot near the rim.
Ntilikina (NYK) makes incidental contact with Doncic (DAL) on the perimeter.
Ntilikina (NYK) is moving alongside Doncic's (DAL) path and he maintains a legal guarding position as he defends the driving shot attempt.
Doncic (DAL) commits a take foul on Barrett (NYK).
Randle (NYK) and Porzingis (DAL) make incidental contact with one another during rebounding.
Porzingis (DAL) commits a take foul on Randle (NYK).
Barrett (NYK) legally contests Hardaway Jr.'s (DAL) jump shot attempt.
Doncic (DAL) commits a take foul on Gibson (NYK).
Ntilikina (NYK) legally contests Doncic's (DAL) jump shot attempt.
Powell (DAL) commits a take foul on Randle (NYK).
Randle (NYK) engages with Powell (DAL) but does not affect his ability to retrieve the rebound.
